Fr. Spyridon Bailey became the biggest face of Orthodox Christianity online by just making vids talking in a forest called like "OVERCOMING OUR FEAR OF MARTYRDOM". Zero polemics, zero debating, no endless yabbering on cultural issues, no shilling. Just "THE HEART AND TEMPTATION".
Lesson in here. No need to push yourself into the marketplace of idle chatter. Just do your own thing and as long as your heart is in the game people will come and listen.
